mod.name: emojify-channel
mod.value:
A command that adds an emoji to the channel name, be warned you can only use emojify on a channel between 5 minute intervals.
`<prefix>emojify-channel <UnicodeEmoji>`

mod.name: lockdown
mod.value:
A command that locks down the entire server preventing users from joining to protect a guild against a targeted raid.
`<prefix>lockdown`

mod.name: resolve-lockdown
mod.value:
A command that removes the lockdown on the server if the lockdown exists.
`<prefix>resolve-lockdown`

mod.name: prune-roles
mod.value:
A command that deletes all the roles with the name `new role`.
`<prefix>prune-roles`

mod.name: set-topic
mod.value:
A command that sets the topic of the current channel.
`<prefix>set-topic`

mod.name: toggle-captcha
mod.value:
A command that toggles the server captcha. 
`<prefix>toggle-captcha`

mod.name: reaction-role
mod.value:
A command that creates a reaction role. 
`<prefix>reaction-role`

mod.name: get-rr-count
mod.value:
A command that gets the reaction role count of a server. 
`<prefix>get-rr-count`

mod.name: set-logs
mod.value:
Sets the current channel to the server log channel. 
`<prefix>set-logs`

misc.name: invite
misc.value:
A command to invite this bot.
`<prefix>invite`

misc.name: ping
misc.value:
A command to check the latency between the bot server and your server.
`<prefix>ping`

misc.name: help
misc.value:
A command that brings up this dialogue.
`<prefix>help`

misc.name: uptime
misc.value:
A command that tells you the amount of time the bot has been up.
`<prefix>uptime`

misc.name: server-count
misc.value:
A command that tells you the amount of servers the bot is in.
`<prefix> server-count`

misc.name: toggle-gif-filter
misc.value:
A command that toggles the no no gif filter.
`<prefix>toggle-gif-filter`

text.name: ascii
text.value:
A command that converts text to ascii.
`<prefix>ascii <Text>`

text.name: ascii-cyan
text.value:
A command that converts text to cyan colored ascii.
`<prefix>ascii-cyan <Text>`

text.name: ascii-gold
text.value:
A command that converts text to gold colored ascii.
`<prefix>ascii-gold <Text>`

text.name: poll
text.value:
A command that creates an advanced poll. 
`<prefix>poll [<Title>] (<Option1>) (<Option 2>)..`

config.name: setprefix
config.value:
A command that sets the prefix of the bot in the server.
`<prefix>setprefix <NewPrefix>`

config.name: prefix
config.value:
A command that gets the current prefix of the bot in the server.
`<prefix>prefix`
